# Home Program – Lumbar PT Exercises

---

## 1. Quadruped Train Tracks
**Frequency:** 1x Daily / 7x Weekly  
**Sets:** 2 | **Reps:** 15

### Setup
Begin on your hands and knees with a towel or yoga block under one of your knees. Hands under shoulders and knees under hips.

### Movement
Lift the working knee off of the ground until your knees are parallel, then lower your knee back down.

### Tips
- The elevated leg will remain stationary throughout the movement.
- Keep your toes on the ground.
- If you need more support in your wrists, try making a fist and elevating up onto your knuckles.

